New Records: David Willey took 3-56, including 100th ODI wicket
Key Match Events: Haris c Stokes b Woakes 35 (244 all out)
Pre-Game Insights: Steven Finn: 'I think it is a misconception when you hear how softly Jos Buttler speaks because underneath that he is fiercely competitive'
Post-Match Reflections: Jos Buttler: 'It's nice to put in a good performance. It probably sinks in more right now. There's lots to reflect on.'
Ben Stokes: 'People will be frustrated and a bit flabbergasted at the way things have gone.'
David Willey: 'It was a nice way to finish. It would have been nice to go out on a high but for me personally to perform and enjoy the last few games, get to 100 wickets is special for me.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: England will finish seventh in the table with three wins
Pakistan are fifth, just two points off the top four
A second successive fifth-placed finish at a World Cup for Pakistan
